  "detailed_description": "<strong>Between Life & Darkness</strong> is a small indie puzzle game about loss. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111020/extras/1566d355c0a3106d8e47b0b7ff38e5d0.avif?t=1724865955\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About BLAD</h2>The central concept revolves around two worlds: the Dark Side and the Bright Side. You move 'boxes' (flower pots) across these two interconnected worlds, solving puzzles to unblock your path and navigate through them—and through life. All of this is accompanied by a rich story and a great soundtrack.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Between Life & Darkness</strong> is a small indie puzzle game about loss. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111020/extras/1566d355c0a3106d8e47b0b7ff38e5d0.avif?t=1724865955\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About BLAD</h2>The central concept revolves around two worlds: the Dark Side and the Bright Side. You move 'boxes' (flower pots) across these two interconnected worlds, solving puzzles to unblock your path and navigate through them—and through life. All of this is accompanied by a rich story and a great soundtrack.",
